HEADWORD: Saurognathous
<hw>Sau*rog"na*thous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ a
lizard + <?/ the jaw.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having the bones of
